OL,3,CDebt and despair - the Oldham
OL,4,Cresidents locked out of their fire-
OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,FITV News Granada Reports Correspondent
OL,8,FTim Scott
OL,10,FResidents of an unsafe apartment block
OL,11,Fare still paying thousands of pounds
OL,12,Fof management fees for flats they
OL,13,Faren't allowed to live in.
OL,15,FThe Victory Apartments in Oldham were
OL,16,Fdeemed a fire hazard in 2020, and
OL,17,Fresidents were quickly evacuated.
