OL,3,CDebt and despair - the Oldham
OL,4,Cresidents locked out of their fire-
OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,FFive years on, repairs are still
OL,8,Fongoing and they have yet to return;
OL,9,Fbut that hasn't stopped management
OL,10,Fcompany RMG from continuing to charge
OL,11,Fthem for management fees.
OL,13,FFozia Malik is at the end of her
OL,14,Ftether, forced to live in student
OL,15,Fhalls while she waits to move back in.
OL,17,FShe said: "They just send us invoices
OL,18,Fevery year - four to five thousand
OL,19,Fpounds, and they say 'we are doing
OL,20,Fthis, we are doing that' and add more
OL,21,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
