OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,F"I've paid more than #25,000 I think.
OL,8,FWhen every year goes by that we don't
OL,9,Fget answers from RMG, we ask for a
OL,10,Ftime frame but don't get one."
OL,12,FLee Ashworth and his daughter Sarah
OL,13,Fown and rented out two of the flats
OL,14,Fhere, and together they have lost
OL,15,Fthousands to RMG and paid thousands
OL,16,Fmore in rent.
OL,18,FLee's been diagnosed with Leukemia and
OL,19,Fhis wife has a serious brain condition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
